# Solana Core workflow

- **Source of truth for code:** Local clone path in **`scripts/solana-repo.config.js`** (default **`../other-projects/solana`**). Override with **`LOCAL_REPO_PATH`** when running **`node scripts/check-solana-changes.js`**.
- **After pulling Solana:** Run **`node scripts/check-solana-changes.js`** (no args) to see changed paths since **`common/solana-last-synced.txt`** (or `main`). Re-read affected **`solana-core/**/*.html`** prose and links; extend **`PREFIX_HINTS`** in the script as modules specialize.
- **Baseline:** After edits, **`node scripts/check-solana-changes.js --save`** stores current Solana HEAD for the next diff — same pattern as hyperscale-rs.
- **Glossary:** Link **`../../common/glossary.html`** (or **`../common/glossary.html`** from nested folders). Shared styles/scripts live under **`common/`**.
- **Course layout:** Three modules per level. **Level 1** is reading-only. **Levels 2+** mirror Hyperscale: **two reading modules + one OSS contribution module** per level (purple card on `solana-core/index.html`).
